<p> </p>
<pre>
Right hand frame: SHADE/Z=0:180/X=0/L=1 flow_on_depth</pre><p> </p>
<div class="dnd-atom-wrapper type-image context-sdl_editor_representation" contenteditable="false">
<div class="dnd-drop-wrapper"><!-- scald=84:sdl_editor_representation --><div class='image'><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://ferret.pmel.noaa.gov/Ferret/sites/default/files/thumbnails/image/along_channel.png" width="1177" height="588" alt="along_channel.png" title="along_channel.png" /></div><!-- END scald=84 --></div>
